Class Paper

  • java.lang.Object
    • Paper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Paper>, java.util.Comparator<Paper>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConferencePaper, JournalPaper

    public class Paper
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<Paper>, java.lang.Comparable<Paper>, java.io.Serializable
    The Paper class for Paper objects that are imported into the program through a file, stored into a collection, sorted, searched through, and printed.
    Version:
    1.0
